skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: logic gates
des:
This skill help kids to know about logic gates. It covers 7 logic gates 
i.e AND,OR,NOT,NAND,NOR,EXOR and EXNOR gates. It contains the details of logic gate symbol along with its truth table. Skill would brief about the logic gates and would ask kids to query which logic gate they want to understand. Once kid is done with the understanding ,he/she can ask Alexa to stop.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
